/>"},{"pid":"b512c13ea476a0a058b621e3e086ca0c9f9f40f8","tid":235370,"uid":98386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T04:17:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>見住班人<br />\n0.68 0.69 0.72 係度計黎計去 唔講以為你兌幾百萬hkd<br />\n直接升返十唔撚洗計 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n起碼少班窮𨶙去日本都好，依家亞豬亞狗重要等平機票先去，好那肉酸。去到日本後呢班窮𨶙又影衰曬啲高質港人。</blockquote><br />\n話明港柒有高尚嫁咩 真係笑死人"},{"pid":"df2b55fea4a0ba4b11ca8adad0f3514939671bc8","tid":235370,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T04:17:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>btw，其實今時今日，日本係窮撚去架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實想去個短trip 五至七日 近近地都冇咩揀 都係泰國同日本</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁係你窮啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想知東南亞邊度高汁 我都唔想再去日本</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講咗你啲死窮撚又阻住我玩<br />\n死返去日本玩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b55545274b1f73b61ddffd7df22deb166554743f","tid":235370,"uid":10682,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T04:20:24.000Z","msg":"成班死毒撚剩係識窮窮地去日本就以為去過全世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75003897fafe077c7f7393e18eaad057ca93ddb3","tid":235370,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T04:25:22.000Z","msg":"去日本？垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a73404f22d2bbccb1728b581e83c4695e84536ad","tid":235370,"uid":80386,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T04:25:56.000Z","msg":"其實慳唔代表窮/低質，闊佬唔代表有錢/高質<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"677b81c99229f290623f5a3e45e2109caebf1929","tid":235370,"uid":30698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T04:27:12.000Z","msg":"唔好搞到要人笑你眼光淺窄啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b9dbb6c8be8e02f9bb014fa850ed8b3716e9039","tid":235370,"uid":27510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T04:28:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  其實點計有錢同無錢?<br />\n<br />\n有人一年去1次 洗左2皮<br />\n有人一年去5次 每次洗1皮<br />\n<br />\n咁邊個有錢?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解會變左睇果個人個trip用左幾錢就決定人有唔有錢<br />\n而且你又無講明呢2條友分別每次去幾多日<br />\n一年去一次，去左一兩日，用左2皮<br />\n同一年去五次，每次去成個星期，每次用1皮<br />\n都唔同講法啦係咪先<br />\n<br />\nbtw唔覺日本有好多野要用到好多錢(可能我窮啦)<br />\n以前未去過，第一次去果陣都帶定左好多錢去，諗住會買好多野<br />\n結果番黎hk果陣用剩好多錢"},{"pid":"3c21aef284d53cce60ebec97a3282414a90229eb","tid":235370,"uid":28549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T04:32:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實慳唔代表窮/低質，闊佬唔代表有錢/高質<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但樓主係講緊連匯率差2%都阿支阿左果種人<br />\n高質極有限<br />\n不過呢種人去到十算都係會去日本<br />\n因為呢種人多數無乜腦<br />\n到時只係會嘈由9.8升到10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f26797895ff4b761e706ad613cce8690cc49630c","tid":235370,"uid":69417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T04:33:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實慳唔代表窮/低質，闊佬唔代表有錢/高質<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets